com.ibm.team.process.common
Interface IItemChangeReport

public interface IItemChangeReport

An item change report reifies modifications to a set of items in the course of the execution of an operation. The item change report carries a list of deleted items, a list of added items, and a list of updated items.

Since:
0.5
